// `emit_collect.vl` — the emitter's COLLECTION passes: the pre-lowering walks
// that fill the shared emitter tables (`emit_state.vl`) before any bytes are
// emitted — function/global gathering + lambda lifting (`collectFns`), closure
// signatures, per-function locals and scratch-slot scans, shape/union/ref-list
// table builds (`collectA`/`collectS`/`collectU`, annotation + anonymous
// shapes), return-kind inference (`computeRetInference`), and the heap-type
// index assignment (`mAssignTypeIndices`). Consults the classifiers
// (`emit_classify.vl`); writes no bytes. Carved out of `wasmEmit.vl`
// (review N18).

